message: First scratch push test
Lots of bug fixes. Added disconnect nodes feature. Still working on adding edges via mermaid parser.
Minimap math working
Fixed Minimap bug. Added corner prop to Minimap and Controls component.
Finally got the Minimap working the way I intended. Very exciting.
Cleanup and comments.
Preparing for release. Clean up.
Reworked path finding algorithm for step edges. Functionality is there, but needs cleanup. Added a more flexible way of specify initial connections.
Refactored touch handling. Fixed anchor state bug.
Bug fixes for launch/merge.
Finished website landing page component. Fixed Group Box bug.
Added node rotation
Package update
Added more flexibility around mixing custom Node elements with node props. Added useDefaults prop.
Changed package.json and removed console logs in preparation for launch
Two way binding with controls, minimap and toggle props.
Optimized bounds recalculation when dragging nodes. Can now move hundreds of Nodes at once. Added fitView prop and fitView functionality to Controls.
Made slight optimization to pinch events. Added touch controls for slider and theme toggle.
Fixed bug related to connection/disconnection event logic firing. Added Playwright test.

Added explicit return type to createStore function and changed structure of store.ts file. Fixed issue where, during the build process, the store types were not being generated and exported properly. Thanks to @rohanrajpal for the assistance.
Renamed NodeConfig type NodeProps. Renamed GraphConfig type GraphProps and moved to graph.ts file. Added initialLocation prop to Svelvet component.
Renamed NodeConfig to NodeProps. Exported GraphProps type. Added translation prop to Svelvet.

Exposed let:destroy on Node component. Re-added width and height as props on Node component to improve compatability with v6. Added useDefaults to NodeProps interface. Added new route to experiment with a function to easily remap edges/nodes from v6 to the new API.
fix: onMount node size calculatin was not accounting for scale.
chore: update package version
Changed NodeProps and GraphProps interface names to NodeConfig and GraphConfig due to conflict with Svelte's internal type exports.
chore: update package version
chore: added husky for lint, format and test pre commit. update prepublishOnly script. code cleanup.
feat: added center prop to node to allow for initial placement in center of viewport. exposed getViewPortCenter function that takes a graph id.
chore: update package version
fix: prevent default logic was blocking pointer events on input elements added to custom nodes

feat: added on:duplicate event to Node component, feat: added GroupBoxes to Minimap, feat: Nodes can be moved with keyboard arrow keys, feat: added Meta + A key command to select all nodes, refactor: removed keypress store, refactor: renamed Minimap Node component, refactor: cleaned up moveNodes function
chore: update all package dependencies
feat: graphs and other components can now be styled using CSS variables and :root[svelvet-theme=theme-name] selectors
fix: bug related to the scheduling of fitView when resize was set to true
refactor: reorganized internal node as an example files structure for other components
chore: update package version and gitignore file
fix: playwright incorrectly listed under dependencies rather than devDependencies
fix: inputs could not be interacted with due to change in keydown listener. added basic test for functionality
feat: nodes can now be resized from all sides, feat: custom nodes that change dimensions dynamically are now supported
fix: specifying anchor connections at node level was not making proper assignments when passing anchors to custom nodes
feat: added drop prop to Node component enabling Nodes to appear at the current relative cursor position on the graph
refactor: changed how resizability was handled with fit content nodes
feat: title attribute is now settable via a prop on the Anchor, Node and Svelvet component
feat: added read only binding to position prop for node
